# None

**Enumeration Case**

Signifies no preferences over what to prioritize when loading the map.

## Declaration

```swift
readonly None: null;
```

## Discussion

In this case, MapKit JS uses its default prioritization, [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/LoadPriority/PointsOfInterest].

## Prioritizations

- **LandCover**: Prioritizes loading of the map land cover and borders, without POIs or labels.
- **PointsOfInterest**: Prioritizes loading of the full standard map, with rendered POIs.
